th>-th expert for input <math id=3D"S2.SS1.p5.3.m3" class=3D"ltx_Math" altt=
ext=3D"X" display=3D"inline" intent=3D":literal"><semantics><mi>X</mi><anno=
tation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">X</annotation></semantics></math>, wh=
ile <math id=3D"S2.SS1.p5.4.m4" class=3D"ltx_Math" alttext=3D"p(Y\mid X,\Th=
eta_{x}^{i})" display=3D"inline" intent=3D":literal"><semantics><mrow><mi>p=
