<section id=3D"S3.SS2.SSS2" class=3D"ltx_subsubsection">
<h4 class=3D"ltx_title ltx_title_subsubsection">
<span class=3D"ltx_tag ltx_tag_subsubsection">3.2.2. </span>Expert Aggregat=
ion and Logit Level Fusion</h4>

<div id=3D"S3.SS2.SSS2.p1" class=3D"ltx_para">
<p id=3D"S3.SS2.SSS2.p1.4" class=3D"ltx_p">We employ a Mixture of Experts f=
ramework in which a router model dynamically selects a subset of specialize=
d expert models for each input instance and integrates their outputs at the=
 logit level. Let <math id=3D"S3.SS2.SSS2.p1.1.m1" class=3D"ltx_Math" altte=
xt=3D"\mathcal{E}=3D\{e_{1},e_{2},\ldots,e_{N}\}" display=3D"inline" intent=
=3D":literal"><semantics><mrow><mi class=3D"ltx_font_mathcaligraphic">=E2=
=84=B0</mi><mo>=3D</mo><mrow><mo stretchy=3D"false">{</mo><msub><mi>e</mi><=
mn>1</mn></msub><mo>,</mo><msub><mi>e</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>,</mo><mi ma=
thvariant=3D"normal">=E2=80=A6</mi><mo>,</mo><msub><mi>e</mi><mi>N</mi></ms=
ub><mo stretchy=3D"false">}</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding=3D"appli=
cation/x-tex">\mathcal{E}=3D\{e_{1},e_{2},\ldots,e_{N}\}</annotation></sema=
ntics></math> denote a set of <math id=3D"S3.SS2.SSS2.p1.2.m2" class=3D"ltx=
_Math" alttext=3D"N" display=3D"inline" intent=3D":literal"><semantics><mi>=
N</mi><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">N</annotation></semantics>=
</math> expert models, where each expert <math id=3D"S3.SS2.SSS2.p1.3.m3" c=
lass=3D"ltx_Math" alttext=3D"e_{j}" display=3D"inline" intent=3D":literal">=
<semantics><msub><mi>e</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><annotation encoding=3D"applica=
tion/x-tex">e_{j}</annotation></semantics></math> is trained as a binary cl=
assifier and produces two output logits corresponding to the non-vulnerable=
 and vulnerable classes. Given an input code fragment <math id=3D"S3.SS2.SS=
S2.p1.4.m4" class=3D"ltx_Math" alttext=3D"x_{i}" display=3D"inline" intent=
=3D":literal"><semantics><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><annotation encod=
ing=3D"application/x-tex">x_{i}</annotation></semantics></math>, the router=
 model outputs a probability distribution over the experts,</p>
<table id=3D"S3.Ex1" class=3D"ltx_equation ltx_eqn_table">

<tbody><tr class=3D"ltx_equation ltx_eqn_row ltx_align_baseline">
<td class=3D"ltx_eqn_cell ltx_eqn_center_padleft"></td>
