/msub></msub><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">e_{k_{i,m}}</annota=
tion></semantics></math> produces a logit vector <math id=3D"S3.SS2.SSS2.p3=
.3.m3" class=3D"ltx_Math" alttext=3D"\boldsymbol{\ell}_{i,k_{i,m}}\in\mathb=
