 class=3D"ltx_mathvariant_bold" mathvariant=3D"bold">=E2=84=93</mi><mrow><m=
i>i</mi><mo>,</mo><msub><mi>k</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>m</mi></mro=
w></msub></mrow></msub><mo>=E2=88=88</mo><msup><mi>=E2=84=9D</mi><mn>2</mn>=
</msup></mrow><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">\boldsymbol{\ell}_=
{i,k_{i,m}}\in\mathbb{R}^{2}</annotation></semantics></math>, representing =
unnormalized scores for the two output classes. The final expert aggregated=
 representation for input <math id=3D"S3.SS2.SSS2.p3.4.m4" class=3D"ltx_Mat=
