.</span>, <a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2603.13213v1#bib.bib29" title=
=3D"Resource-efficient algorithms and systems of foundation models: a surve=
y" class=3D"ltx_ref">2025</a>; Gordon<span class=3D"ltx_text ltx_bib_etal">=
 et al.</span>, <a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2603.13213v1#bib.bib76" t=
itle=3D"Compressing bert: studying the effects of weight pruning on transfe=
r learning" class=3D"ltx_ref">2020</a>; Xu<span class=3D"ltx_text ltx_bib_e=
tal"> et al.</span>, <a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2603.13213v1#bib.bib=
71" title=3D"Beyond preserved accuracy: evaluating loyalty and robustness o=
f bert compression" class=3D"ltx_ref">2021</a>; Ye<span class=3D"ltx_text l=
tx_bib_etal"> et al.</span>, <a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2603.13213v1=
#bib.bib43" title=3D"Adversarial robustness vs. model compression, or both?=
" class=3D"ltx_ref">2019</a>; Du<span class=3D"ltx_text ltx_bib_etal"> et a=
l.</span>, <a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2603.13213v1#bib.bib82" title=
