guage understanding" class=3D"ltx_ref">2021</a>; Gourtani and Meratnia, <a =
href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2603.13213v1#bib.bib83" title=3D"Improving r=
obustness of compressed models with weight sharing through knowledge distil=
lation" class=3D"ltx_ref">2024</a>; Zhu<span class=3D"ltx_text ltx_bib_etal=
"> et al.</span>, <a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/html/2603.13213v1#bib.bib5" =
title=3D"Safety and performance, why not both? bi-objective optimized model=
 compression toward ai software deployment" class=3D"ltx_ref">2022</a>; Sun=
<span class=3D"ltx_text ltx_bib_etal"> et al.</span>, <a href=3D"https://ar=
xiv.org/html/2603.13213v1#bib.bib88" title=3D"Patient knowledge distillatio=
n for bert model compression" class=3D"ltx_ref">2019</a>; Jiao<span class=
