/html/2603.13213v1#bib.bib3" title=3D"Lion: adversarial distillation of pro=
prietary large language models" class=3D"ltx_ref">2023</a>; Zhang<span clas=
s=3D"ltx_text ltx_bib_etal"> et al.</span>, <a href=3D"https://arxiv.org/ht=
ml/2603.13213v1#bib.bib85" title=3D"StructADMM: a systematic, high-efficien=
